        <p> I showed him on my cell phone that I wanted to go to the Flying Fish Hostel, he only nodded briefly and then I squeezed my luggage and myself in the passenger seat. After a 5 -minute drive we were already on the hostel. With 100 peso (&euro; 1.50) I probably paid far too much but it didn't matter, because I had finally arrived. </p>
        <p> After checking in, I sat, the rest of the evening with some other travelers and we exchanged stories and tips. There was a self -mixed alster water to drink, which of course caused some ridicule and mockery. But I'm lucky. But now I'm going to run. Good night. </p>
